   <pb facs="98"/>
   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>The starkest foole,</l>
      <l>if well he marke</l>
      <l>This skilfull Schoole,</l>
      <l>prooues greatest clarke.</l>
      <l>Come therefore you</l>
      <l>that wise would be,</l>
      <l>And learne anew,</l>
      <l>this A, B, C.</l>
   </lg>
